descriptionHtml:
Darkwater Estate v1.02
		
		by Wurzelbert

My first mod anyway. When i first saw this location i thought \"somebody MUST build a house there\" so why shouldn´t i give it a try?
If you update to the new version pls be sure to get everything out of the house first.

-------------------------------------------------------
**Info**
This mod adds a player-house in the rift at the upper exterior of the darkwater cave.
All you need for crafting is somewhere in or around the house.
-------------------------------------------------------
**Installation**
To install the mod simply paste the Darkwater Estate.esp to your Skyrim/Data folder
where all the .esp files are.
-------------------------------------------------------
**issues**
This mod will conflict with any mod that modifies the same place.
Sometimes the House doesn´t appear, but the door is there so you can get in. I don´t know why this happens, so if you know why pls tell me.
If you find other issues feel free to contact me :)
-------------------------------------------------------
v1.02 some Bugfixes with weapon racks
v1.01 some Bugfixes with Navmesh
v1.0 Standart file
-------------------------------------------------------


Thx to Bethesda for the great game and the awesome Creation Kit Tutorial _/,,/
author: Wurzelbert
